ields\": {\"title\": \"Write Up\", \"body\": \"<p><strong>Work to be done</strong></p><p>Try to make communication between DSpace and Django using REST calls.&nbsp;</p><p>Make the contents of all types that is published in Django to be available and search-able through DSpace through metadata.</p><p>For this we have to export the publish content from the Django to DSpace.</p><p>Expecting that all the meta-data required for publishing the content must be available in Django.</p><p>? Whether the publishing of content should be done immediately or scheduled.</p>\", \"image\": \"\", \"created_at\": \"2018-02-07T10:27:13.430Z\", \"created_by\": 8, \"views\": 0, \"state\": 1}}]','Write Up',19,5,'default'),(8,'3','json','[{\"model\": \"Group.grouparticles\", \"pk\": 3, \"fields\": {\"article\": 3, \"user\": 12, \"group\": 5}}]','GroupArticles object',21,6,'default'),(9,'3','json','[{\"model\": \"BasicArticle.articles\", \"pk\": 3, \"fields\": {\"title\": \"Writeup for notification\", \"body\": \"<p>Notification works involves implementation of following tasks:</p><p>1.) When a new user is added in the group then all members of that group should get a notification when they login.</p><p>2.) When an article gets modified then all users who are working on that article should get a notification for the same.</p>\", \"image\": \"\", \"created_at\": \"2018-02-07T10:59:58.819Z\", \"created_by\": 12, \"views\": 0, \"state\": 1}}]','Writeup for notification',19,6,'default'),(10,'4','json','[{\"model\": \"Group.grouparticles\", \"pk\": 4, \"fields\": {\"article\": 4, \"user\": 12, \"group\": 5}}]','GroupArticles object',21,7,'default'),(11,'4','json','[{\"model\": \"BasicArticle.articles\", \"pk\": 4, \"fields\": {\"title\": \"Writeup\", \"body\": \"<p>Following tasks need to be implemented for notification:</p><p>1.) When a user is added to a group then all current users should get a notification for the same.</p><p>2.) When an article gets modified then all owners of the article should get notified.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p>\", \"image\": \"article/f212cfeb-1b79-4150-83d8-89497cd8402c.jpg\", \"created_at\": \"2018-02-07T11:04:52.276Z\", \"created_by\": 12, \"views\": 0, \"state\": 1}}]','Writeup',19,7,'default'),(12,'5','json','[{\"model\": \"BasicArticle.articles\", \"pk\": 5, \"fields\": {\"title\": \"Phase 0 - Work Description and Agenda\", \"body\": \"<p>sdbckjbsd</p>\", \"image\": \"\", \"created_at\": \"2018-02-07T11:05:06.805Z\", \"created_by\": 9, \"views\": 0, \"state\": 1}}]','Phase 0 - Work Description and Agenda',19,8,'default'),(13,'5','json','[{\"model\": \"Group.grouparticles\", \"pk\": 5, \"fields\": {\"article\": 5, \"user\": 9, \"group\": 3}}]','GroupArticles object',21,8,'default'),(14,'5','json','[{\"model\": \"BasicArticle.articles\", \"pk\": 5, \"fields\": {\"title\": \"Phase 0 - Work Description and Agenda\", \"body\": \"<p>The following is the description of the work to be done to create dynamic and customizable workflow of any content in Collaborative community project.</p>\", \"image\": \"\", \"created_at\": \"2018-02-07T11:05:06.805Z\", \"created_by\": 9, \"views\": 1, \"state\": 1}}]','Phase 0 - Work Description and Agenda',19,9,'default'),(15,'5','json','[{\"model\": \"BasicArticle.articles\", \"pk\": 5, \"fields\": {\"title\": \"Phase 0 - Work Description and Agenda\", \"body\": \"<p>The following is the description of the work to be done to create dynamic and customizable workflow of any content in Collaborative community project.</p><p>Work-flow of any content refers to the change of states that any content go through during its life cycle.</p><p>For example,</p><ul><li>Any article from the moment of its creation, belongs to \'draft\' state</li><li>Only from \'draft\' state can an article be made \'publishable\' by authors.</li><li>Similarly, only after an article is made \'publishable\' it can be published (moved to \'published\' state).</li><li>An article can be deleted only from \'draft\' state. Hence, once an article is made \'publishable\' or \'published\', it cannot be deleted. Also, no article can be recovered after deleting.</li></ul>\", \"image\": \"\", \"created_at\": \"2018-02-07T11:05:06.805Z\", \"created_by\": 9, \"views\": 1, \"state\": 1}}]','Phase 0 - Work Description and Agenda',19,10,'default'),(16,'6','json','[{\"model\": \"BasicArticle.articles\", \"pk\": 6, \"fields\": {\"title\": \"Writeup - Reputation System\", \"body\": \"<p>A reputation system should automatically assign a rank to every new user and have a system to promote them based on their contributions. &nbsp;A user will have different reputation for each community. &nbsp;The admin of a community should be able to promote or demote a user on will. &nbsp; The admin should also be able to set criteria for automatic promotion of a user. &nbsp; We will need some predefined set of ranks (Beginner, Novice etc) and a model for how much points should be given for each contribution. (5 pts for Article etc)&nbsp;</p>\", \"image\": \"article/43b819e9-e4d4-4383-840f-f4bb64201b80.jpg\", \"created_at\": \"2018-02-07T11:07:48.356Z\", \"created_by\": 13, \"views\": 0, \"state\": 1}}]','Writeup - Reputation System',19,11,'default'),(17,'6','json','[{\"model\": \"Group.grouparticles\", \"pk\": 6, \"fields\": {\"article\": 6, \"user\": 13, \"group\": 7}}]','GroupArticles object',21,11,'default'),(18,'5','json','[{\"model\": \"BasicArticle.articles\", \"pk\": 5, \"fields\": {\"title\": \"Phase 0 - Work Description and Agenda\", \"body\": \"<p>The following is the description of the work to be done to create dynamic and customizable workflow of any content in Collaborative community project.</p><p>Work-flow of any content refers to the change of states that any content go through during its life cycle.</p><p>For example,</p><ul><li>Any article from the moment of its creation, belongs to \'draft\' state</li><li>Only from \'draft\' state can an article be made \'publishable\' by authors.</li><li>Similarly, only after an article is made \'publishable\' it can be published (moved to \'published\' state).</li><li>An article can be deleted only from \'draft\' state. Hence, once an article is made \'publishable\' or \'published\', it cannot be deleted. Also, no article can be recovered after deleting.</li></ul><p>Thus any article or other content type can follow certain predefined sequences of states. More clearly, a particular state can be reached only from one of its possible previous states and can lead to one of its possible next states.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><h4>&nbsp;</h4>\", \"image\": \"\", \"created_at\": \"2018-02-07T11:05:06.805Z\", \"created_by\": 9, \"views\": 1, \"state\": 1}}]','Phase 0 - Work Description and Agenda',19,12,'default'),(19,'5','json','[{\"model\": \"BasicArticle.articles\", \"pk\": 5, \"fields\": {\"title\": \"Phase 0 - Work Description and Agenda\", \"body\": \"<p>The following is the description of the work to be done to create dynamic and customizable workflow of any content in Collaborative community project.</p><p>Work-flow of any content refers to the change of states that any content go through during its life cycle.</p><p>For example,</p><ul><li>Any article from the moment of its creation, belongs to \'draft\' state</li><li>Only from \'draft\' state can an article be made \'publishable\' by authors.</li><li>Similarly, only after an article is made \'publishable\' it can be published (moved to \'published\' state).</li><li>An article can be deleted only from \'draft\' state. Hence, once an article is made \'publishable\' or \'published\', it cannot be deleted. Also, no article can be recovered after deleting.</li></ul><p>Thus any article or other content type can follow certain predefined sequences of states. More clearly, a particular state can be reached only from one of its possible previous states and can lead to one of its possible next states.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><h4